<h2>1. How does ordering work?</h2>
<p style="font-size: 1.2rem">1.1. If you already have a model you want to get printed, you can either use my print calculator, or just dm me on discord or send me an email. After payment I will print the file, send you a picture of the printed product and send you the print.</p>
<p style="font-size: 1.2rem">1.2. If you want a custom design, you can dm me on discord or send me an email. We will discuss the design and the price. After payment I will start designing and printing the product. I will send you pictures of the design and if everything will be OK, i will print it and send it to you.</p>
<p style="font-size: 1.2rem">1.3. If you want to buy a model from the shop, you can dm me on discord or send me an email. After payment I will print the model and send it to you. In the future there will be a digital storefront, where you will simply pay, and the model will get printed and shipped.</p>

<h2>2. How do I pay?</h2>
<p style="font-size: 1.2rem">2.1. As of today, you can pay with PayPal, bank transfer or crypto (ether, btc, monero and more). There will be more payment methods in the future.</p>

<h2>3. How do I get my print?</h2>
<p style="font-size: 1.2rem">3.1. I will send you a picture of the printed product. If you are satisfied with the print, I will send it to you either via Packeta, or the post local office. Depending on where you are located. Shipping from Prague, CZ.</p>
<p style="font-size: 1.2rem">3.2. If you are based in Prague, CZ, we can arrange personal pickup.</p>

<h2>4. Returns</h2>
<p style="font-size: 1.2rem">4.1. Returns of custom printed items accepted (return shipping paid by the customer) only in case of abnormal material failure or shipping defects, due to everything being discussed personally beforehand. If you are unsatisfied with the print, tell me before I ship it and I will refund you the money.</p>

<h2>5. Large orders</h2>
<p style="font-size: 1.2rem">5.1. If you want to order a large(r) amount of prints, we can arrange a significant discount, custom material colors etc.</p>

<h2>6. Print information</h2>
<p style="font-size: 1.2rem">6.1. I print with PLA, PETG, TPU, ABS, ASA, PC and more.</p>
<p style="font-size: 1.2rem">6.2. I can print in a variety of colors, check on print calculator or on discord server. If you are willing to cover the costs, I can buy filament just for your print.</p>
<p style="font-size: 1.2rem">6.3. My largest print bed is 250x25Omm.</p>


